id: pm-swja
title: "CI: make package test scripts sandbox-first"
description: Align npm scripts and GitHub workflows with the sandboxed PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH test runner so local and CI test commands are safe by default and CI avoids duplicate full coverage runs.
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: agent-ux,ci,pm-cli,testing
