updated_at: "2026-05-02T11:29:45.337Z"
author: codex-agent
acceptance_criteria: "pnpm test and pnpm test:coverage use node scripts/run-tests.mjs; CI workflows skip the extra build inside test scripts after the explicit build step; redundant coverage runs are removed while sandboxed coverage remains enforced; workflow contract tests are updated."
parent: pm-ote
resolution: Package test scripts and GitHub workflows now use sandbox-first test execution without duplicate full coverage runs.
expected_result: "Local pnpm test commands and CI gates preserve PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH isolation while keeping build, typecheck, coverage, security, packaging, and release gates intact."
actual_result: "pnpm test/test:coverage call node scripts/run-tests.mjs; workflows skip the internal rebuild after explicit build and rely on the sandboxed coverage gate; focused contract tests and full coverage passed."
